    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master precision platforming in Memori, a game built from the ground up for speedrunners and casual players alike. Frame-perfect controls meet intricate level design in a world where every millisecond counts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712700/extras/9cea399da62f4db571efaee80fe86343.poster.avif?t=1754454890\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712700/extras/9cea399da62f4db571efaee80fe86343.webm?t=1754454890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712700/extras/9cea399da62f4db571efaee80fe86343.mp4?t=1754454890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712700/extras/8740324e3af6b6f9892bef1fa3ec6cf0.poster.avif?t=1754454890\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712700/extras/8740324e3af6b6f9892bef1fa3ec6cf0.webm?t=1754454890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712700/extras/8740324e3af6b6f9892bef1fa3ec6cf0.mp4?t=1754454890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Built for Speed.</strong> Every input is instant. Every mechanic is consistent. Whether you're hunting for world records or perfecting your personal best, Memori's engine delivers the precision you demand. Input buffering, coyote time, and momentum conservation - all tuned for optimal play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712700/extras/d9e385e2968ea771b78fedb703d5b189.poster.avif?t=1754454890\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712700/extras/d9e385e2968ea771b78fedb703d5b189.webm?t=1754454890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712700/extras/d9e385e2968ea771b78fedb703d5b189.mp4?t=1754454890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Compete at Every Level.</strong> Race against ghosts, climb global and friends leaderboards, and chat with other players right in the game. Track your progress with detailed stats showing deaths, completion times, and route analytics. Level editor and Steam Workshop support coming soon!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712700/extras/f97a00b267e5af9fab3d86e8fbb014b6.poster.avif?t=1754454890\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712700/extras/f97a00b267e5af9fab3d86e8fbb014b6.webm?t=1754454890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712700/extras/f97a00b267e5af9fab3d86e8fbb014b6.mp4?t=1754454890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Active Development. Real Updates.</strong> This isn't a &quot;release and forget&quot; game. Regular updates based on community feedback. New tech discoveries become official features. Your routes and strategies shape the game's evolution.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712700/extras/dec0b515307c4e2cca48ce170e0aeacb.poster.avif?t=1754454890\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712700/extras/dec0b515307c4e2cca48ce170e0aeacb.webm?t=1754454890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712700/extras/dec0b515307c4e2cca48ce170e0aeacb.mp4?t=1754454890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frame-perfect precision controls - No input lag, no physics randomness</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Integrated speedrun tools - In-game timer, splits, ghost runs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Comprehensive leaderboard system - Global rankings, friends leaderboards, ghost replays, and in-game chat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Personal stats tracking - Deaths, completion times, route analytics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple routes per level - Reward creativity and optimization</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Active developer updates - New features based on community discoveries</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level editor and Steam Workshop support (coming soon)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >cats</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712700/extras/7cf9968c9bc55410d0497b555e1c8ea7.poster.avif?t=1754454890\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712700/extras/7cf9968c9bc55410d0497b555e1c8ea7.webm?t=1754454890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712700/extras/7cf9968c9bc55410d0497b555e1c8ea7.mp4?t=1754454890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
